<p>TinyMCE allows us to list groups of styles. For example, the following would display a list of classes applied to DIVs or Ps.</p>  <pre><code>{title: 'Block styles', filter: /^(div|p)\./} </code></pre>  <p>I'd like to display a list of classes which:</p>  <pre><code>- contain the word 'image'  - contain the word 'img'  - or are prefix by the tag img. </code></pre>  <p>But I can't figure out the regex to do it :(</p>  <p>Any suggestions?</p>